creator: dotnamics
descriptionHtml:
The official SPOT Festival app

In this app you can:

See the program for the festival. The program is updated automatically as we release new concerts, movies, seminars, etc. The program can be sorted by band name, venue and date, and you can choose to only show concerts or movies or seminars – or a mix.

Discover every artist, band, seminar and movie in depth. Read more, jump to relevant webpages and so on.

Create your own program: which concerts are you going to hear, which movies to watch, which seminars to participate in? Save your favourites in the app and avoid forgetting any of them.

Read the latest news from the festival. News is updated in the app as they are announced.

See all the practical informations about the festival: transport to and from the festival area, where to buy ticket etc.

See a map of the festival area, so you have an overview of all the venues, seminar rooms and so on.

About SPOT Festival:
SPOT Festival is a unique showcase-festival, which has been conducted for the last 21 years in Aarhus.
SPOT presents music, movies, interactive and seminars from Denmark and the rest of Scandinavia that has artistic potential – also in an international perspective.
Concerts and more are introduced to both a Danish and an international audience.
descriptionShort: The official SPOT Festival app. Program, news, lineup and much more.
